nected with each other by means of Peptide bond. It is the outcome of Multi-Amino Acid “hand in hand”. Peptide is related with various fields, including human hormone, nerves, cell growth and reproduction etc. It’s significance consists in regulating various systems and cellular physiological function in vivo, activating relevant enzymatic system in vivo，promoting permeability of intermediary metabolism membrane, or affect differential protein synthesis through controlling DNA transcord to bring about specific physiological effect finally. Scientists call over 10 hand-in-hand Amino Acids as polypeptide, whereas the less than 10 hand-in-hand Amino Acids as small Peptide, which is called also small molecule active Peptide and “biological active Peptide” as generic term.\nVEG VALLEY Peptide is just the small molecule Peptide，among which the one, which amount of molecular weight is within 5000-500 Dalton occupies 8% of the total and the one less than 500 Dalton occupies 72%.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">After protein enzymatic hydrolysis through alimentary tract, its absorption is mainly by means of the mode with small Peptide type, and its absorption is even easier and faster than that with completely free Amino Acid. Peptide is not only able to supply nutrient substances required by human body for growth and development, but also possessed of unique biological function, can prevent and cure thrombosis, hypertension, as well as to postpone aging, resist fatigue and enhance immunity of the organism.</p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The dermal metabolic cycle of human body is 28 days (regenerated cell comes up to horny layer from stratum basale). The active constituent of peptide could get rid of dermal injury caused by free radical and be able to activate manifold biochemical enzyme, so as to achieve the objective to induce cell growth through starting up endonuclear cytokinesis chain cable. It could promote cytokinesis，regulate Collagen metabolism，accelerat