(155, 1, '2016-07-21 10:13:13', '2016-07-21 10:13:13', 'Is the miraculous change to be witnessed? Yes, it needs a week only!\r\n<h3>What is Collagen?</h3>\r\nCollagen is a kind of extracellular protein, the spiral fibrous protein formed with 3 twisted Peptide chains.\r\nThe Collagen is the most abundant protein containing in human body and occupies above 30% of the total proteins in the whole body. The Collagen contains abundant Amino Acids, including Glycine , Proline, Oxyproline etc that are required by human body, as well as the foremost constituent parts in extracellular matrix.\r\nThere is about 3kg Collagen in an adult body, the Collagen consists mainly in the skin, bones, eyes, teeth, muscle tendons, viscera (including heart, stomach, intestine and blood vessel) etc of human body. The function thereof is to maintain the shape and structure of skin and tissue organs, and it’s also the vital raw material substance for restoring various injured tissue.\r\n<h3>The efficacy of Collagen:</h3>\r\nThe Collagen is the essential component in the skin of human body, occupies 72% in the skin and 80% in derma. The Collagen forms a sheet of fine mesh elasticated net to lock up moisture, as if a bracket to sustain skin. It makes cytoplasm plumpy, moisture sufficient, as well as makes skin full of elasticity, moist, fineness and smoothness. In the skin, Collagen is a “spring”, responsible for dermal elasticity and degree of consolidation. It’s a “reservoir” as well, responsible for dermal moisture content and moisture storage capacity. Collagen is responsible directly for the degree of moisture embellish, smoothness, degree of compactness of skin, as well as “skin age”.\r\n<h3>The advantages of Collagen to skin represent concretely in the following several aspects:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Moisturizing:</strong> Collagen contains hydrophilic natural moisturizing factors; moreover, its three spiral structure is able to lock up moisture intensively, so as to keep skin moi