able. It could promote cytokinesis，regulate Collagen metabolism，accelerate the formation of epithelia tissue, bring melanin out of skin, and it would flake along with the natural exfoliation of aging died horn cells (scurf). Dermal epidermal base is provided with phagocyte, able to phagocytize melange granules and make them drained out of human body along with normal excretion, so as to fade color spots making skin fair, fine, tender and lustering. Peptide could also promote Collagen generation and metabolism of transition cells, consummate formation of collagen tissue and incrassation of connective tissue, as well as lock up moisture in skin tightly to increase dermal elasticity and dispel fine wrinkle on face.\r\nIt’s indicates in contemporary nutriology research findings that after protein is taken into human body, it would be absorbed by human body when it’s decomposed into small molecule protein Peptides and Amino Acid, among which the protein in the mode of Peptide absorbed by human body occupies above 70% of the total amount of the absorbed protein. At bottom, the human body in vivo is to absorb protein by means of the approach to absorb Peptide and Amino Acid, and Peptide is the upmost protein ingredient for the absorption. Therefore, the most primary indicator for measuring protein quality is to see the digestible degree of protein, the level of its absorption by human body, the degree of protein utilization, as well as to see whether the content of essential amino acid is abundant, whether it’s complete in variety and adequate in proportion.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="tab-content-page" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n\r\n[vegvalley_function_block]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container content">\r\n<h3>Beauty treatment functions of VEG VALLEY Peptide:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Activation of histiocyte — Allow skin to coruscate youth energy;</li>\r\n 	<li>Eliminate free radical — Allow skin to be even more beautiful, white, fine and tender;</li>\r\n 	<li