(213, 1, '2016-07-27 07:24:45', '2016-07-27 07:24:45', '<div class="container content">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Is the miraculous change to be witnessed? Yes, it needs a week only!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;">What is Collagen?</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Collagen is a kind of extracellular protein, the spiral fibrous protein formed with 3 twisted Peptide chains.\r\nThe Collagen is the most abundant protein containing in human body and occupies above 30% of the total proteins in the whole body. The Collagen contains abundant Amino Acids, including Glycine , Proline, Oxyproline etc that are required by human body, as well as the foremost constituent parts in extracellular matrix.\r\nThere is about 3kg Collagen in an adult body, the Collagen consists mainly in the skin, bones, eyes, teeth, muscle tendons, viscera (including heart, stomach, intestine and blood vessel) etc of human body. The function thereof is to maintain the shape and structure of skin and tissue organs, and it’s also the vital raw material substance for restoring various injured tissue.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;">The efficacy of Collagen:</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Collagen is the essential component in the skin of human body, occupies 72% in the skin and 80% in derma. The Collagen forms a sheet of fine mesh elasticated net to lock up moisture, as if a bracket to sustain skin. It makes cytoplasm plumpy, moisture sufficient, as well as makes skin full of elasticity, moist, fineness and smoothness. In the skin, Collagen is a “spring”, responsible for dermal elasticity and degree of consolidation. It’s a “reservoir” as well, responsible for dermal moisture content and moisture storage capacity. Collagen is responsible directly for the degree of moisture embellish, smoothness, degree of compactness of skin, as well as “skin age”.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: justify;">The advantages of Collagen to skin represent concretely in the following several aspects:</h3>\r\n<ul style="text-align: justify;">\r\n 	<li><strong>Moisturizing: </strong>Collagen contains hydrophilic natural moisturizing factors; moreover, its three spiral structure is able to lock up moisture intensively, so as to keep skin moist constantly.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Nourishing:</strong> Active Collagen has strong penetrability to skin. it could permeate cuticle and combine with epithelia to participate in and change the metabolism of dermal cells and strengthen the activity of the Collagen in the skin. It’s able to hold the moisture in cuticle and keep the integrality of fiber structure, change the living environment of dermal cells, and promote the metabolism of dermal tissue, enhance blood circulation, and satisfy the requirement for moistening skin.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Skin lightening:</strong> Dermal lightness rests with moisture content. The all-right water retaining capacity of Collagen makes skin moisture embellish and glossy and emitting gloss.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Skin tightening:</strong> After Collagen is absorbed by skin，it could be filled in between skin and derma, so as to increase the degree of skin tightening and result in skin tension, sweat pore reduction to make skin stretching tight with high resilience.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Anti-wrinkle:</strong> The plump Collagen layer in derma for sagging skin combines with moisturizing and wrinkle restraining effect to achieve jointly the functions and results to stretch coarse wrinkles and fade fine wrinkles.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Skin restoration:</strong> Active Collagen is able to penetrate directly into skin stratum basale with its excellent affinity with neighboring tissues and assist cells to form into Collagen, so as to urge skin cell growing up normally. Meanwhile，active Collagen is provided by itself with the effects of anti-inflammation and skin renewal.\r\nWhen Collagen is insufficient, not only skin and bones could go wrong, but also adverse effect on